data.title: Diamond Princess Intro
data.meta_description: Discover all the secrets of the Diamond Princess, a state-of-the-art ship offering a wide variety of activities and leisure on board.
data.text: Diamond Princess is a treasure trove of exceptional delights waiting to be discovered. Dine on freshly prepared sashimi in Kai Sushi, watch street performers in the dazzling Atrium, or take in a lavish production show in our state-of-the-art theater. And for a unique treat visit the Izumi Japanese Bath, the largest of its kind at sea.
